MPI CORP (6223)  said unconsolidated sales
in April fell 42.18% to NT$216,549,000 from NT$374,553,000,
according to a statement filed to the  Taiwan Stock Exchange .  (Figures are in thousands of New Taiwan dollars)  =================================================================  4/2012           4/2011
Sales            216,549          374,553    
YOY%             -42.18%   -----------------Year-to-date-----------------
Sales            691,579         1,386,331   
YOY%             -50.11% 
=================================================================
 